DESCRIPTION:Holiday-flavored improv from Southside Sidekicks\, the Guild's
  in-house comedy troupe — scenes made up on the spot.\n\nImprov comedy f
 rom the Southside Sidekicks\, the in-house troupe of Southside Theatre Gui
 ld\, this time with a naughty-or-nice seasonal spin. Nothing is scripted: 
 the performers build scenes and characters from audience suggestions\, so 
 the show that happens is the one the room helps make.
